videos.description: Kansas' Frank Mason III tips the inbounds pass and makes the steal, then gets fouled to make two huge free throws to give the Jayhawks a 109-106 win over Oklahoma.
videos.headline: Mason steals inbounds pass in triple OT

videos.description: Buddy Hield puts up a contested 3-pointer that misses long, which puts an end to Kansas' 109-106 win over Oklahoma in triple overtime.
videos.headline: Hield's last-second shot doesn't go

videos.description: Minutes after Oklahoma's 109-106 loss to Kansas in triple overtime, Buddy Hield joins SVP to discuss his emotions and to break down the little things that didn't work for the Sooners.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Interview (Buddy Hield on loss to Kansas) 2016/01/04 SVP SC

videos.headline: Hield: 'I just need a bed right now'

videos.description: Kansas fans give Oklahoma's Buddy Hield a standing ovation after Hield scores 46 points in a losing effort.

videos.description: Jeff Goodman joins SVP to break down whether Frank Mason III's steal off Buddy Hield late in the third overtime of Kansas' victory over Oklahoma was a legal play.
